{"tid":2179550,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[介紹]輕度策略型手遊 決戰EGM！","createTime":"2020-08-29T07:45:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T16:31:11.000Z","uid":366710,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f307276f913ea008f2225f94fe1c821a1bda7f6b","tid":2179550,"uid":366710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T07:45:55.000Z","msg":"今天想為大家介紹的是一款以未來城市作為背景的塔防遊戲，這遊戲的主要玩法是在16方格中去生成像素機甲消滅小怪。而遊戲而PVP模式作為賣點，遊戲機制是每當我方消滅了一隻小怪，對方就會生成一隻，反之亦然。所以只要比對方消滅得更快就能從中獲勝！機制有點像Tetris的battle mode一樣。喜歡策略遊戲的玩家絕對不要錯過哦！ <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Od5j6ad.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOd5j6ad.jpg&h=c87c0166&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而且遊戲的晝風十分精美，是非常精美的美少女立繪，目前總共擁有8個角色，各有各的技能及能力，不同的角色會對你的戰局有著不同的影響哦！不論你是蘿莉或禦姐控，總有一款會合你心水！每個角色不僅立繪絢麗， 還有不同的屬性加成，為戰局提供關鍵性幫助！(以下是我有的兩款角色orz)<br />\n遊戲中會有著不同的升級道具可供玩家選購，透過購買更高級/不同屬性的機甲就可以大大加強玩家的實力。此外，遊戲除了PVP模式以外，還有合作、故事和競技場模式可供遊玩！而且還有不同的機甲活動，我個人覺得耐玩性也蠻高的，算是一款輕度的策略類型遊戲，在坐車的時候玩一兩局也是非常好的選擇！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xfete3R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxfete3R.png&h=9678e9c7&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4kwrMaw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4kwrMaw.png&h=033610a3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n遊戲中有著不同的機甲，各有著不同的能力，類別有分成攻擊、輔助和控制。透過玩家自由的搭配就<br />\n有著不同的效果，而且變化也蠻多的，幾乎不會沈悶！而且有一直想要玩下去的衝勁！(要升Rank嘛XD)，遇到強人的時候會有種想要打敗他的感覺！<br />\n附上遊玩片段！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eC8T8K2NrMg&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DeC8T8K2NrMg%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=aJB%2Bq6ruafnyRbkwc%2FW5Zubr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=b1d8a419\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eC8T8K2NrMg&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\nApp Store連結<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DBNZmKH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDBNZmKH.jpg&h=119fc2de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nGoogle Playstore連結<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GJ2yrbt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGJ2yrbt.jpg&h=2356b964&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6b3a8886b922c881532f604264b2f4f06497d4aa","tid":2179550,"uid":82450,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T07:59:30.000Z","msg":"抄驚就返屋企啦，屌你老母仲要係支那公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e4db68b7882c2c9d73a4477d0791efbb6a84741","tid":2179550,"uid":126133,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T08:10:45.000Z","msg":"唔夠膽講明抄random dice就話玩法似其他game<br />\n笑死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4dcd89c500a3490e1dadd9e81670a0b8d3149cf","tid":2179550,"uid":366710,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"6b3a8886b922c881532f604264b2f4f06497d4aa","tid":2179550,"uid":82450,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T07:59:30.000Z","msg":"抄驚就返屋企啦，屌你老母仲要係支那公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T16:17:30.000Z","msg":"個原創者係香港人黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係大陸架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"327d6e55a3306ad11dda8a07e6c2952ce991f33d","tid":2179550,"uid":24559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T14:00:55.000Z","msg":"有簡體字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"991e9a8b521f2d389f8c2c998a9cbc5b05ecdabb","tid":2179550,"uid":155374,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f307276f913ea008f2225f94fe1c821a1bda7f6b","tid":2179550,"uid":366710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T07:45:55.000Z","msg":"今天想為大家介紹的是一款以未來城市作為背景的塔防遊戲，這遊戲的主要玩法是在16方格中去生成像素機甲消滅小怪。而遊戲而PVP模式作為賣點，遊戲機制是每當我方消滅了一隻小怪，對方就會生成一隻，反之亦然。所以只要比對方消滅得更快就能從中獲勝！機制有點像Tetris的battle mode一樣。喜歡策略遊戲的玩家絕對不要錯過哦！ <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Od5j6ad.jpg\" 